<!--BODY-->
<body>
  <%- include('partials/header') %>
<!--MAIN DESIGN-->
             
<main>

  <section class="home-carousel-section">
    <div class="home-carousel-container">
      
      <!-- Mitad izquierda: carrusel de imágenes -->
      <div class="home-carousel-images">
        <img src="images assessment/Mediterranean Artist in Creative Sanctuary.jpeg" alt="Art 1" class="home-carousel-slide active">
        <img src="images assessment/Vibrant Neon Fashion.jpeg" alt="Art 2" class="home-carousel-slide">
        <img src="images assessment/Urban Photographer in Focus.jpeg" alt="Art 3" class="home-carousel-slide">
        <img src="images assessment/Dynamic Motion Blur with Colorful Attire.jpeg" alt="Art 4" class="home-carousel-slide">
  
        <!-- Flechas opcionales -->
        <button class="home-carousel-prev" onclick="prevSlide()">&#10094;</button>
        <button class="home-carousel-next" onclick="nextSlide()">&#10095;</button>
      </div>
  
      <!-- Mitad derecha: texto -->
      <div class="home-carousel-text">
        <h1>SOLENT ART UNIVERSITY</h1>
        <p>Where creativity meets excellence – inspiring your artistic journey every step of the way.</p>
      </div>
  
    </div>
  </section>
  
    <!-- Nueva sección destacada de Solent Art University -->
    <section class="solent-highlight">
        <div class="highlight-box">
            <h1>
                <span class="solent">Why</span>
                <span class="art">Choose </span>
                <span class="university">Solent Art?</span>
            </h1>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Sección informativa -->
   
    <section class="info-section">
        <div class="info-container">
            <h2></h2>
            <p>Studying at Solent Art University means joining a vibrant community where creativity, innovation, and passion come together. With a strong focus on both undergraduate and postgraduate programs, the university offers a dynamic environment to develop artistic talent and professional skills. Our state-of-the-art facilities, experienced tutors, and industry connections help students thrive in real-world creative industries. Whether you're beginning your journey or advancing your expertise, Solent is the place to grow and succeed.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>
   

    <!-- Secciones de razones para entrar a Solent Art University -->
<section class="reason-section">
    <div class="reason-box">
      <h2 class="reason-title">History</h2>
      <p class="reason-text">Founded in 1838 to meet the demands of the evolving textile industry and its expanding global trade, our institution stands as one of the country's oldest art schools and the oldest design school in Britain, proving our long-standing commitment to art education.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reason-box">
      <h2 class="reason-title">Build your Network </h2>
      <p class="reason-text">Collaboration is at the heart of what we do, so we have an array of open spaces, not only for you to explore on your own, but to watch, listen and learn from those working in other disciplines. You’ll connect with the industry, either through visiting guest speakers, work experience or live briefs to enrich your learning and develop your employability skills.</p>
    </div>
  
    <div class="reason-box">
      <h2 class="reason-title">Placement Oportunities</h2>
      <p class="reason-text">Across our art and design courses we have opportunities for you to visit international exhibitions and access international study programmes, offering you a comprehensive and enriching education.</p>
    </div>
  
    <div class="reason-box">
      <h2 class="reason-title">Build your Network </h2>
      <p class="reason-text">Collaboration is at the heart of what we do, so we have an array of open spaces, not only for you to explore on your own, but to watch, listen and learn from those working in other disciplines. You’ll connect with the industry, either through visiting guest speakers, work experience or live briefs to enrich your learning and develop your employability skills.</p>
    </div>
  
    <div class="reason-box">
      <h2 class="reason-title">Placement Oportunities</h2>
      <p class="reason-text">Across our art and design courses we have opportunities for you to visit international exhibitions and access international study programmes, offering you a comprehensive and enriching education.</p>
    </div>
  
    <div class="reason-box">
      <h2 class="reason-title">Industry Standard Facilities</h2>
      <p class="reason-text">Our RIBA award-winning Lowry building provides an ambitious inter-connected art and design complex. It features a vertical gallery, hybrid studio spaces and a multitude of workshops that include ceramics, jewellery design, bookbinding, traditional and digital printing, and more</p>
    </div>
  
    <div class="reason-box">
      <h2 class="reason-title">Successful Alumni</h2>
      <p class="reason-text">During our history, we have seen many of our graduates go on to be nationally and internationally renowned artists, designers, filmmakers or photographers. Graduates include Sarah Burton OBE, L.S. Lowry, Sylvia Pankhurst, Julie Walters, Steve Coogan, and many more. </p>
    </div>

    <div class="reason-box">
        <h2 class="reason-title">Creative Empowerment and Global Achievement</h2>
        <p class="reason-text">Solent Art University nurtures values of authenticity, inclusion, and artistic commitment. Its practical and human-centered approach has led students to win international awards and lead creative projects worldwide. Here, every student’s success is celebrated as part of a collective journey</p>
      </div>
  </section>

         <!-- 2da sección: 3 Boxes -->
  <section class="three-boxes">
    <div class="box"><img src="images assessment/Group Portrait Against Orange Background.jpeg" alt="Art Gallery"></div>
    <div class="box"><img src="images assessment/Group Portrait with Orange Background.jpeg" alt="Student Workshop"></div>
    <div class="box"><img src="images assessment/Unity and Strength.jpeg" alt="Campus Life"></div>
  </section>
        <!-- mision and vission-->

  <section class="home-vision-mission-box">
    <h2>Our Vision & Mission</h2>
    <div class="vision-mission-buttons">
      <button onclick="showVision()">Vision</button>
      <button onclick="showMission()">Mission</button>
    </div>
    <div id="visionText" class="vision-mission-text" style="display: none;">
      <p>To be a leading institution of creative excellence, empowering students to shape the future of the arts and culture industry.</p>
    </div>
    <div id="missionText" class="vision-mission-text" style="display: none;">
      <p>To provide high-quality education, inspire innovation, and nurture the creative potential of every student in a diverse and inclusive environment.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

        <!-- motivationtext -->

  <section class="home-motivation-text">
    <h2>Study at Solent Art University</h2>
    <p>At Solent Art University, we believe in your creative journey. Our programs are designed to inspire, challenge, and prepare you for a fulfilling career in the arts. Join a vibrant community of artists and thinkers, and take your passion to the next level. Your future starts here.</p>
  </section>

